/target
# eBPF objects build to their own target dir under the git-ignored root target
**/target/
**/*.rs.bk
.env
.env.local
*.log
# Built/downloaded VM images (guest kernel + rootfs) — fetched by `cargo xtask fetch-artifacts`,
# never committed.
/artifacts/
# The local vendor mirror of all sha-pinned upstream inputs (`cargo xtask vendor`) — a self-hoster
# produces it to build offline; like /artifacts/ it holds downloaded images, never committed.
/vendor/
# Local .md files
MASTER.md
LOCAL.md
LAUNCH.md

# mdBook output (`mdbook build docs`) — the book renders from the committed docs/*.md
/docs/book/
# cargo-fuzz working data (the `fuzz/` crate is excluded from the workspace; `fuzz/target` is already
# covered by `**/target/` above). Corpora and crash artifacts are generated, not committed.
/fuzz/corpus/
/fuzz/artifacts/
/fuzz/coverage/
